     C                   EVAL      SUFRCDN=ZXCOUNT                                                  
     C                   ENDIF                                                                      
                                                                                                    
     C                   IF        INDPRO1=*OFF                                                     
     C                   CLEAR                   PSUCUST                                            
     C*                  CLEAR                   PSUDLG1                                            
     C                   ENDIF                                                                      
                                                                                                    
     C                   IF        INDPRO2=*OFF                                                     
     C*                  CLEAR                   PSUDLG2                                            
     C                   CLEAR                   PSUTPED                                            
     C                   ENDIF                                                                      
09022C                   IF        INDPRO3=*OFF                                                     
09022C                   CLEAR                   PSUFPED                                            
09022C                   ENDIF                                                                      
                                                                                                    
