PG615 * ChkCustomer                                                                                 
PG615 *  Valida flag bloquejos per Albará, a nivell de client                                       
PG615 *-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------    
PG615c     ChkCustomer   begsr                                                                      
PG615 *                                                                                             
PG615c                   eval      bLckAlb   =*off                                                  
PG615 *                                                                                             
PG615c     kcoclin       chain     coclin                                                           
PG615c                   if        s0babb='1'                                                       
PG615c                   eval      bLckAlb   =*on                                                   
PG615c                   else                                                                       
PG615c                   eval      bLckAlb   =*off                                                  
PG615c                   endif                                                                      
PG615 *                                                                                             
PG615c                   endsr                                                                      
